attributes.Long form description: The student changes the battery and the SD card of the GoPro.The student turns the GoPro on and off; after that, the student assembles the strap and then changes it to the tripod. The student changes the tripod to the handheld grip. In the end, the student disassembles the handheld grip.

attributes.Transcription: Hello, thank you for agreeing to take part in our study.The task in front of you will be using the GoPro action camera.
First, can you please change the battery in the camera?
You will find the battery compartment on the right side of the camera.
It will be on the opposite side of the camera.
To open the battery compartment, please slide the notch in the lower part of the side downwards.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student presses instead of pulling the battery.

attributes.Transcription: It's pull it the battery using basic tab.
Next, please change the micro SD card in the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student changes the SD card.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please turn on the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns the GoPro on.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please turn off the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns the GoPro off.

attributes.Conversation Purpose: instructor-start-conversation_adjusting to capture better quality video
attributes.Transcription: Please make sure both of your hands are front of you.
Next, please mount the shoulder strap on the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student mounts the strap on the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please switch the mounted GoPro camera from the shoulder mount to the tripod.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the strap with the tripod.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please change the mount on the camera from the tripod mount to the handheld grip.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the tripod with the handheld grip.

attributes.Conversation Purpose: instructor-start-conversation_adjusting to capture better quality video
attributes.Transcription: Please make sure both of your hands look on the camera.
Please push the camera and make sure that the is aligned with the handheld.
Lastly please remove the handheld mode from the GoPro and place everything on the table.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the handheld grip for the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: You now press the stop button because is everything.
